* Clone into ~/.vim: `git clone git@github.com:fvisin/vim.git ~/.vim`

* Run:
    ```
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    git submodule foreach git submodule init
    git submodule foreach git submodule update
    cd bundle/YouCompleteMe
    git submodule update --init --recursive
    ./install.sh
    ```

* Install python flake8 or any other syntax checker allowed by syntastic

* Install jedi: `pip install jedi`

* Copy vimrc or vimrc_lisa in ~/.vimrc

* Read the vimrc docstring to learn about the shortcuts keys to the tools
